Reasoning: The paper deals with crowdsourcing tasks and algorithms for decision-making based on worker quality scores. This suggests that it could belong to the Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) category, as well as the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) category. The use of data analysis and simulation also suggests that it could belong to the Cybernetics (cs.CY) and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) categories. Finally, the use of algorithms and decision-making could also place it in the Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) category.
